My Accessibility Buddy - Alt-Text Report

MyAccessibilityBuddy is an AI-powered tool for generating WCAG 2.2 compliant alternative text for web images. It supports 24 EU languages with several LLMs: OpenAI GPT-4o, ECB-LLM like GPT-4o and GPT-5.1.

For testing purposes only: Use with non confidential images. Avoid uploading personal or sensitive data. AI suggestions require human review before use.
